        <heading>Public notice and hearing procedures</heading>
        <content>
          <p>ยง 15-0807. Public notice and hearing procedures.\n  The promulgation of rules and regulations pursuant to this title shall\nbe exclusively governed by the rule-making procedures of the state\nadministrative procedure act, except that municipalities affected by the\nreleases which are the subject of such rules and regulations shall also\nbe provided an opportunity for consultation during the preparation of\nsuch rules and regulations.\n</p>
